{
  "stem": "25938.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "About that, I remember once with a conversation with my brother, he said there was anti-Semitism in my town.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I myself didn't experience.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't-- it was not such-- I didn't experience any persecution or something in Poland.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But-- but I felt we lived a different life.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were isolated, Jewish people were.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We lived-- we-- we-- we spoke a different language.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We-- life was based on religious customs and all these things.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I forgot, what was the topic?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Acts of-- Anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Did you feel that the-- that the isolation was inflicted upon you?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Or did you feel that it was self--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, the--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The people were-- people were polite and we'd actually-- my mother actually was born in a village, and the best-- our best-- when I was about six years old, five years old, our best friend was a Jewish peasant, a Jewish lady-- a non-Jewish lady.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The name by [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Jurza. ?] We called her aunt, Aunt [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Jurza. ?] And so my mother spoke perfect white Russian.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She was a blond.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she mingled with the-- with the-- with peasant people, with ladies.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so and she was liked by-- by the-- by the population, by the non-Jewish, the peasants.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They used to buy the-- what do you-- what do you say it in English?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The dye that you-- that you're dying, that--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But there was-- there was a very subtle hostility.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In school, in the public school, we all sometimes from the-- from the Polish boys, Christ killer.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You're a Christ killer.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then let's say, once a year, when they used to go from the church with the ceremony, they called it, you know when the-- the-- birthday of Jesus.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What do you call that-- that-- that name?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
